# VHS tape — regenerate with: vhs assets/citations.tape
Output assets/citations.gif

Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1000
Set Height 540
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 38ms
Set Padding 12

Type "# Does AI actually cite your brand? Ask it directly."
Sleep 1.5s
Enter
Type "geo citations --brand 'GeoReady' --domain geoready.dev --topic 'GEO audit tools'"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 28s
Sleep 3s
